<scriptment id="94000" point="hanako_shop" localizationstatus="original" fictionaldate="2011-11-22" status="final">
	<part>
		<narration>A flower shop. Petunias litter the nearby ledges. Vines hang from the front sign. Petals flow through the open door.</narration>
		<line id="1000" speaker="hanako" voicelang="ja">Isn't it beautiful, Yuki?</line>
		<line id="2000" speaker="yuki" voicelang="ja">I don't really care for JPEG.</line>
		<narration><comment>Zoom out.</comment>It's a picture.</narration>
		<line id="3000" speaker="game">flowershop.jpeg</line>
		<narration>Yuki and Hanako stand before the future site of the flower shop: a cellphone store.</narration>
		<line id="4000" speaker="yuki" voicelang="ja">So you're expecting this cellphone store to tank?</line>
		<line id="5000" speaker="hanako" voicelang="ja">Yeah!</line>
		<line id="6000" speaker="hanako" voicelang="ja">Cellphones are a luxury industry.</line>
		<narration><comment>Flash a game-box.</comment>Video games are a luxury industry.</narration>
		<line id="7000" speaker="hanako" voicelang="ja">The company is going bankrupt.</line>
		<narration>Sega is going bankrupt.</narration>
		<line id="8000" speaker="hanako" voicelang="ja">Larger, more same-landed companies are threatening them.</line>
		<narration>Larger, more same-landed companies are threatening Sega.</narration>
		<line id="9000" speaker="hanako" voicelang="ja">When they close this shop down, I'll start up my flower store.</line>
		<line id="10000" speaker="hanako" voicelang="ja">Since you're so cute when you make decisions,</line>
		<line id="11000" speaker="hanako" voicelang="ja">I'll let you decide a partner in crime for this shop.</line>
		<condition>
			<choice number="1">
				<line id="12000" speaker="yuki" voicelang="ja">Dan.</line>
			</choice>
			<choice number="2">
				<line id="13000" speaker="yuki" voicelang="ja">Ganpu.</line>
			</choice>
			<choice number="3">
				<line id="14000" speaker="yuki" voicelang="ja">Takuya.</line>
			</choice>
			<choice number="4">
				<line id="15000" speaker="yuki" voicelang="ja">Lori.</line>
			</choice>
		</condition>
		<narration>Hanako raises an eyebrow.</narration>
	</part>
</scriptment>